    }
\end{tikzpicture}
```

### Step 3: Interpret the FEN Notation
The FEN notation consists of several parts:
- `rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1` for example
